#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.fbeta_score.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.fbeta\\_score"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:1 of
msgid "Compute the F-beta score"
msgstr "计算 F-beta 分数"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:3 of
msgid ""
"The F-beta score is the weighted harmonic mean of precision and recall, "
"reaching its optimal value at 1 and its worst value at 0."
msgstr "F-beta 分数是精确率和召回率的加权调和平均数，其最佳值为 1，最差值为 0。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:6 of
msgid ""
"The `beta` parameter determines the weight of recall in the combined "
"score. ``beta < 1`` lends more weight to precision, while ``beta > 1`` "
"favors recall (``beta -> 0`` considers only precision, ``beta -> +inf`` "
"only recall)."
msgstr ""
"`beta` 参数决定了组合分数中召回率的权重。``beta < 1`` 会更重视精确率，而 "
"``beta > 1`` 更偏向召回率（``beta -> 0`` 只考虑精确率，``beta -> +inf`` "
"只考虑召回率）。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:11 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <precision_recall_f_measure_metrics>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <precision_recall_f_measure_metrics>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:13 of
msgid "Ground truth (correct) target values."
msgstr "真实（正确）的目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:15 of
msgid "Estimated targets as returned by a classifier."
msgstr "由分类器返回的估计目标。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:17 of
msgid "Determines the weight of recall in the combined score."
msgstr "决定组合分数中召回率的权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:19 of
msgid ""
"The set of labels to include when ``average != 'binary'``, and their "
"order if ``average is None``. Labels present in the data can be excluded,"
" for example to calculate a multiclass average ignoring a majority "
"negative class, while labels not present in the data will result in 0 "
"components in a macro average. For multilabel targets, labels are column "
"indices. By default, all labels in ``y_true`` and ``y_pred`` are used in "
"sorted order."
msgstr ""
"当 ``average != 'binary'`` 时要包含的标签集合，以及当 ``average is None``"
" 时它们的顺序。数据中存在的标签可以被排除，例如在计算多类平均值时忽略多数"
"负类；而数据中不存在的标签在宏平均中会导致 0 成分。对于多标签目标，标签是"
"列索引。默认情况下，``y_true`` 和 ``y_pred`` 中的所有标签将按排序顺序使用"
"。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:27 of
msgid ""
"The class to report if ``average='binary'`` and the data is binary. If "
"the data are multiclass or multilabel, this will be ignored; setting "
"``labels=[pos_label]`` and ``average != 'binary'`` will report scores for"
" that label only."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``average='binary'`` 且数据是二分类的，则报告该类别。如果数据是多类"
"或多标签的，则此参数将被忽略；设置 ``labels=[pos_label]`` 和 ``average !="
" 'binary'`` 将只报告该标签的分数。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:32 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"This parameter is required for multiclass/multilabel targets. If "
"``None``, the scores for each class are returned. Otherwise, this "
"determines the type of averaging performed on the data:  ``'binary'``:"
"     Only report results for the class specified by ``pos_label``.     "
"This is applicable only if targets (``y_{true,pred}``) are binary. "
"``'micro'``:     Calculate metrics globally by counting the total true "
"positives,     false negatives and false positives. ``'macro'``:     "
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted     mean.  "
"This does not take label imbalance into account. ``'weighted'``:     "
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their average weighted     by "
"support (the number of true instances for each label). This     alters "
"'macro' to account for label imbalance; it can result in an     F-score "
"that is not between precision and recall. ``'samples'``:     Calculate "
"metrics for each instance, and find their average (only     meaningful "
"for multilabel classification where this differs from     "
":func:`accuracy_score`)."
msgstr ""
"此参数对多类/多标签目标是必需的。如果为 ``None``，则返回每个类别的分数。"
"否则，它决定在数据上执行的平均类型：  ``'binary'``:     只报告由 ``pos_"
"label`` 指定类别的结果。     仅适用于目标（``y_{true,pred}``）为二分类的"
"情况。 ``'micro'``:     通过计算总的真正例、假负例和假正例来全局计算指标"
"。 ``'macro'``:     为每个标签计算指标，并求其未加权平均值。     不考虑"
"标签不平衡。 ``'weighted'``:     为每个标签计算指标，并按支持度（每个标签"
"的真实实例数）加权平均。     这会修改 'macro' 以考虑标签不平衡；可能导致 "
"F-score 不在精确率和召回率之间。 ``'samples'``:     为每个实例计算指标，"
"并求其平均值（仅在多标签分类中与 :func:`accuracy_score` 不同的情况下有"
"意义）。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:32 of
msgid ""
"This parameter is required for multiclass/multilabel targets. If "
"``None``, the scores for each class are returned. Otherwise, this "
"determines the type of averaging performed on the data:"
msgstr ""
"此参数对于多类/多标签目标是必需的。如果为 ``None``，则返回每个类的分数。"
"否则，这将确定在数据上执行的平均类型："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:36 of
msgid "``'binary'``:"
msgstr "``'binary'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:37 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Only report results for the class specified by ``pos_label``. This is "
"applicable only if targets (``y_{true,pred}``) are binary."
msgstr ""
"仅报告由 ``pos_label`` 指定的类的结果。这仅适用于目标（``y_{true,pred}``"
"）为二进制的情况。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:39 of
msgid "``'micro'``:"
msgstr "``'micro'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:40 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics globally by counting the total true positives, false "
"negatives and false positives."
msgstr "通过计算总的真正例、假负例和假正例来全局计算指标。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:42 of
msgid "``'macro'``:"
msgstr "``'macro'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:43 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted mean.  This "
"does not take label imbalance into account."
msgstr "计算每个标签的指标，并找到它们的未加权平均值。这不会考虑标签不平衡。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:45 of
msgid "``'weighted'``:"
msgstr "``'weighted'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:46 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their average weighted by "
"support (the number of true instances for each label). This alters "
"'macro' to account for label imbalance; it can result in an F-score that "
"is not between precision and recall."
msgstr ""
"计算每个标签的指标，并根据支持度（每个标签的真实实例数量）进行加权平均。"
"这会修改 'macro' 以考虑标签不平衡；可能会导致F分数不在精确率和召回率之间"
"。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:50 of
msgid "``'samples'``:"
msgstr "``'samples'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:51 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each instance, and find their average (only "
"meaningful for multilabel classification where this differs from "
":func:`accuracy_score`)."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:55 of
msgid "Sample weights."
msgstr "样本权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:57 of
msgid ""
"Sets the value to return when there is a zero division, i.e. when all "
"predictions and labels are negative. If set to \"warn\", this acts as 0, "
"but warnings are also raised."
msgstr ""
"设置当出现零除错误时返回的值，即当所有预测和标签都为负时。如果设置为 \""
"warn\"，则其作用为 0，但也会发出警告。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:62 of
msgid ""
"**fbeta_score** -- F-beta score of the positive class in binary "
"classification or weighted average of the F-beta score of each class for "
"the multiclass task."
msgstr ""
"**fbeta_score** -- 二分类中正类的 F-beta 分数，或多类任务中每个类别的 F-"
"beta 分数的加权平均。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.fbeta_score:66 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`precision_recall_fscore_support`, "
":py:obj:`multilabel_confusion_matrix`"
msgstr ""

